Photo shared by poets of instagram on August 09, 2021 tagging @rafpoetry. May be a black-and-white image of text that says 'Some days I have nothing to say. Not to myself, not to anybody else. There is an awkward silence in me confused about sharing itself with anyone else. All I can do is listen to myself, pacify myself. Because these are the days I desperately feel the need to be loved. And there's nothing wrong in it. raf'.

node.text:
Loving the power and truth in this 💬⠀
(cr: @rafpoetry)
